# [KMS](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/general/latest/gr/kms.html#limits_kms)

Default quotas:
- Cryptographic operations (symmetric) request rate [**CryptographicOperationsSymmetric**]: 20,000 per second , Auth quota 20,000 per second
- Cryptographic operations (RSA) request rate [**CryptographicOperationsRsa**]: 1000 per second, Auth quota 5000 per second
- Cryptographic operations (ECC) request rate [**CryptographicOperationsEcc**] : 1000 per second, Auth quota 10,000 per second
